// ... existing imports ...
import { 
  Button,
  List,
  ListItem,
  ListItemText,
  ListItemIcon,
  Divider
} from '@mui/material';
import {
  Add as AddIcon,
  Person as PersonIcon,
  Assignment as AssignmentIcon,
  BusinessCenter as BusinessIcon
} from '@mui/icons-material';

const Dashboard = () => {
  // ... existing state and functions ...

  return (
    <Box sx={{ p: 3 }}>
      {/* ... existing stat cards ... */}

      <Grid container spacing={3} sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Paper sx={{ p: 2, height: '100%' }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Recent Activity
            </Typography>
            <List>
              <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <PersonIcon color="primary" />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText 
                  primary="New Customer Added"
                  secondary="John Doe - Tech Solutions Inc."
                />
              </ListItem>
              <Divider />
              <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <AssignmentIcon color="warning" />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText 
                  primary="Lead Status Updated"
                  secondary="Project X - Status changed to Qualified"
                />
              </ListItem>
              <Divider />
              <ListItem>
                <ListItemIcon>
                  <BusinessIcon color="success" />
                </ListItemIcon>
                <ListItemText 
                  primary="Deal Closed"
                  secondary="ABC Corp - $50,000"
                />
              </ListItem>
            </List>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
          <Paper sx={{ p: 2, height: '100%' }}>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Quick Actions
            </Typography>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', gap: 2 }}>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<AddIcon />}
                onClick={() => navigate('/customers/new')}
              >
                Add New Customer
              </Button>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<AddIcon />}
                onClick={() => navigate('/leads/new')}
              >
                Create New Lead
              </Button>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                startIcon={<AssignmentIcon />}
                onClick={() => navigate('/leads')}
              >
                View All Leads
              </Button>
            </Box>
          </Paper>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Dashboard;
